FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions? We've got answers to help you make the most of our food app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How do I place an order using the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Simply browse our menu, select your desired items, add them to your cart, and proceed to checkout. Follow the prompts to confirm your delivery address and payment method.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards, PayPal, and mobile wallets. You can securely save your preferred payment method for faster checkout.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How can I track my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Once your order is confirmed, you can track its status in real-time through the 'Order Tracking' feature in the app. You'll receive notifications for order updates and estimated delivery time.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Are there any loyalty rewards or discounts available?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes! We offer a loyalty program where you earn points on every purchase. These points can be redeemed for discounts on future orders. Keep an eye out for special promotions and daily deals in the app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How do I leave a review or provide feedback?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: After receiving your order, you'll have the option to rate your experience and leave a review directly in the app. Your feedback helps us improve our service and assists other users in making informed choices.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our food app allows you to browse local restaurants, view menus, place orders, and track deliveries all in one convenient platform. Simply download the app, create an account, and start exploring delicious options in your area.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is there a minimum order amount?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Minimum order amounts may vary depending on the restaurant. You can easily see any minimum order requirements on each restaurant's page before placing your order.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How can I track my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Once your order is confirmed, you can track its status in real-time through the app. You'll receive updates on when the restaurant accepts your order, when it's being prepared, and when it's out for delivery.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Delivery fees may apply and can vary based on factors such as distance and restaurant policies. The exact fee will be clearly displayed before you complete your order, ensuring full transparency.
